OL,4,Cexposes 'significant amount' of
OL,5,Capplicant data
OL,7,FThe government first became aware of a
OL,8,Fcyber attack on the agency's online
OL,9,Fdigital services on 23 April, but
OL,10,Fdiscovered on Friday that it was more
OL,11,Fextensive than originally thought.
OL,13,FThe MoJ is urging anyone who has
OL,14,Fapplied for legal aid since 2010 to be
OL,15,Falert for unknown messages and phone
OL,16,Fcalls and to update any passwords that
OL,17,Fcould have been exposed.
