OL,4,Cexposes 'significant amount' of
OL,5,Capplicant data
OL,7,FAn MoJ source put the breach down to
OL,8,Fthe "neglect and mismanagement" of the
OL,9,Fprevious government, saying
OL,10,Fvulnerabilities in the Legal Aid
OL,11,FAgency systems have been known for
OL,12,Fmany years.
OL,14,F"This data breach was made possible by
OL,15,Fthe long years of neglect and
OL,16,Fmismanagement of the justice system
OL,17,Funder the last government.
