OL,7,FLegal Aid Agency chief executive Jane
OL,8,FHarbottle apologised for the breach.
OL,10,F"I understand this news will be
OL,11,Fshocking and upsetting for people and
OL,12,FI am extremely sorry this has
OL,13,Fhappened," she said.
OL,15,F"Since the discovery of the attack, my
OL,16,Fteam has been working around the clock
OL,17,Fwith the National Cyber Security
OL,18,FCentre to bolster the security of our
OL,19,Fsystems so we can safely continue the
OL,20,Fvital work of the agency.
