OL,7,F"However, it has become clear that, to
OL,8,Fsafeguard the service and its users,
OL,9,Fwe needed to take radical action. That
OL,10,Fis why we've taken the decision to
OL,11,Ftake the online service down," she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FMs Harbottle said contingency plans
OL,15,Fare in place to make sure those in
OL,16,Fneed of legal support and advice can
OL,17,Fcontinue to access it.
